{"id":157,"ayahs":[{"number":52,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ جِئْنَٰهُم بِكِتَٰبٍۢ فَصَّلْنَٰهُ عَلَىٰ عِلْمٍ هُدًۭى وَرَحْمَةًۭ لِّقَوْمٍۢ يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"for, indeed, We did convey unto them a divine writ which We clearly, and wisely, spelled out - a guidance and a grace unto people who will believe.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1006.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":49669,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49670,"position":2,"arabic":"جِئْنَـٰهُم","translation":"তাদের কাছে আমরা এসেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49671,"position":3,"arabic":"بِكِتَـٰبٍۢ","translation":"নিয়ে এক কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49672,"position":4,"arabic":"فَصَّلْنَـٰهُ","translation":"আমরা বিশদ বর্ণনা করেছি তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49673,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর ভিত্তি করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49674,"position":6,"arabic":"عِلْمٍ","translation":"(পূর্ণ)  জ্ঞানের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49675,"position":7,"arabic":"هُدًۭى","translation":"পথ নির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49676,"position":8,"arabic":"وَرَحْمَةًۭ","translation":"ও দয়া (স্বরূপ)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49677,"position":9,"arabic":"لِّقَوْمٍۢ","translation":"জন্যে সম্প্রদায়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49678,"position":10,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"(যারা) ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_052_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":49679,"position":11,"arabic":"٥٢","translation":"(৫২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":53,"arabic":"هَلْ يَنظُرُونَ إِلَّا تَأْوِيلَهُۥ ۚ يَوْمَ يَأْتِى تَأْوِيلُهُۥ يَقُولُ ٱلَّذِينَ نَسُوهُ مِن قَبْلُ قَدْ جَآءَتْ رُسُلُ رَبِّنَا بِٱلْحَقِّ فَهَل لَّنَا مِن شُفَعَآءَ فَيَشْفَعُوا۟ لَنَآ أَوْ نُرَدُّ فَنَعْمَلَ غَيْرَ ٱلَّذِى كُنَّا نَعْمَلُ ۚ قَدْ خَسِرُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَهُمْ وَضَلَّ عَنْهُم مَّا كَانُوا۟ يَفْتَرُونَ","translation":"Are [the unbelievers] but waiting for the final meaning of that [Day of Judgment] to unfold? [But] on the Day when its final meaning is unfolded, those who aforetime had been oblivious thereof will say: \"Our Sustainer's apostles have indeed told us the truth! Have we, then, any intercessors who could intercede in our behalf? Or could we be brought back [to life] so that we might act otherwise than we were wont to act?\" Indeed, they will have squandered their own selves, and all their false imagery will have forsaken them.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1007.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":50317,"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50318,"position":2,"arabic":"يَنظُرُونَ","translation":"তারা প্রতীক্ষা করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50319,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50320,"position":4,"arabic":"تَأْوِيلَهُۥ ۚ","translation":"পরিণতির তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50322,"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50323,"position":6,"arabic":"يَأْتِى","translation":"আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50324,"position":7,"arabic":"تَأْوِيلُهُۥ","translation":"পরিণতি তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50325,"position":8,"arabic":"يَقُولُ","translation":"বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50326,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_053_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50327,"position":10,"